{"tid":1755511,"cid":31,"subCid":9,"title":"［超突發］發現超高質文宣Facebook page","createTime":"2019-11-25T15:24:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-30T10:59:06.000Z","uid":261134,"like":47,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"ca0baf4489a74a59f5b72bbd8b31b61afb86611c","tid":1755511,"uid":261134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T15:24:14.000Z","msg":"係Facebook見到，有好多文宣手機Wallpaper download, 好多都好高質，佢地叫手提電話連儂牆企劃，大家可以上去睇下：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/GDCSHK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FGDCSHK&d=yZvzIFdj7oCTZXRWgogUmaooFDKVeMyzaQj0gYzwHSI%3D&h=d335d3a2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/GDCSHK</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gBrGAQc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgBrGAQc.jpg&h=1c483825&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n理念：<br />\n偉大的美國平面設計師 David Carson 有一句名言:「Graphic design will save the world right after rock and roll does.」平面設計能不能拯救世界尚且未有定論，但我們現在就要用平面設計來拯救我們居住的地方──香港。<br />\n<br />\n我們將會開始一項名為「Mobile Lennon Wall Project 手提電話連儂牆企劃」，期望能集合香港，以至全球各地的平面設計師來為香港人製作打氣的手提電話桌面，承載著世界對香港人的支持，築成一幅最龐大的連儂牆，不限民族地域為每一位真正的香港人於低潮失望時打打氣。 我們知道這將會是場持久的奮力抗爭，但我們深信只要有意志，力量便無處不在也無遠弗屆。這項企劃希望能時刻勉勵同行的香港人──致勝關建永遠在於堅持和團結。<br />\n<br />\n「不是因為看見希望而堅持，而是因為堅持才看見希望。」我們要相約在煲底振臂高呼，露臉相見。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e5D9KJT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe5D9KJT.jpg&h=db5e7a44&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bKwfFhe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbKwfFhe.jpg&h=66ee1fd0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/22HB9az.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F22HB9az.jpg&h=2206bcc8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gJMvuaz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgJMvuaz.jpg&h=e5cf1e71&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/